  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000305">
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt-br">poço de injeção</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">injection well</rdfs:label>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[ISO 15926-4] An &lt;INJECTION WELL&gt; is  a &lt;WELL&gt; with the purpose of injecting a material into a reservoir, normally with a pressure higher than the formation pressure</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[SLB Glossary] A well in which fluids are injected rather than produced, the primary objective typically being to maintain reservoir pressure.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[OnePetro] A well either specifically drilled, or, more likely, a poor producer that is converted to inject fluids to stabilize the decline of pressure in a productive zone. An injector is required to have a pressure connection to the pay and to a producing well. Water is typically injected at the base of the pay or, in a gas well, or gas is injected into the gas cap.</skos:definition>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en">An injection well is a well that bears the designed function of injecting materials into a reservoir at pressure higher than formation pressure.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="pt-br">Um poço de injeção é um poço que possui a função projetada de injetar materiais em um reservatório a uma pressão superior à pressão da formação.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom xml:lang="en">∀x (InjectionWell(x) ↔ (Well(x) ∧ ∃f (InjectionFunction(f) ∧ bearerOf(x,f))))</iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
    <iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom xml:lang="en">Every injection well is a well that has the function to inject materials into a reservoir under pressure.</iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
    <owl:equivalentClass rdf:nodeID="na2a46d8928414473b41f08b70337d4d1b1990"/>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="na2a46d8928414473b41f08b70337d4d1b3099">
