  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/COPI_0000300">
    <iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom xml:lang="en">∀x (HydraulicPump(x) ↔ PositiveDisplacementPump(x) ∧ ∃f(HydraulicPumpingFunction(f) ∧ bearerOf(x,f)) ∧ ∃p(HydraulicPowerTransmissionProcess(p) ∧ participatesIn(x,p)))</iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[OnePetro] An artificial lift system that is powered by injected fluid (usually water), that powers a pump similar to the rotating pump used in electrical submersible pumps.</skos:definition>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">[ISO 15926-4] A &lt;HYDRAULIC PUMP&gt; is a &lt;POSITIVE DISPLACEMENT PUMP&gt; used in hydraulic drive systems and can be hydrostatic or hydrodynamic. It is a mechanical source of power that converts mechanical power into hydraulic energy (hydrostatic energy i.e. flow, pressure). It generates flow with enough power to overcome pressure induced by the load at the pump outlet. When a hydraulic pump operates, creates a vacuum at the pump inlet, which forces liquid from the reservoir into the inlet line to the pump and by mechanical action delivers this liquid to the pump outlet and forces it into the hydraulic system.</skos:definition>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">hydraulic pump</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt-br">bomba hidráulica</rdfs:label>
    <owl:equivalentClass rdf:nodeID="na2a46d8928414473b41f08b70337d4d1b1896"/>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en">A hydraulic pump is a positive displacement pump that converts mechanical power into hydraulic energy for hydraulic drive systems.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="pt-br">Uma bomba hidráulica é uma bomba de deslocamento positivo que converte energia mecânica em energia hidráulica para sistemas de acionamento hidráulico.</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom xml:lang="en">Every hydraulic pump is a positive displacement pump that bears a hydraulic pumping function and participates in hydraulic power transmission processes.</iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:about="https://www.inf.ufrgs.br/ontologies/copi/BottomOutlet">
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt-br">saída de fundo</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">bottom outlet</rdfs:label>
